{"id": 523, "title": "Ticket #523: Virtual Machine Enhancements", "description": "<blockquote>\nThis ticket outlines plans to improve Virtual Machine support in Condor during the 7.3 development series. Here are the main thrusts with current milestones:\n\n<p></p><ol>\n<li>Dynamically insert jobs into a VM by the startd.\n<ul>\n<li>Design architecture <em>[1 day]</em>\n</li></ul>\n\n<p></p></li><li>Add support for additional virtualization software.\n<ul>\n<li>Build client for SOAP interface of VMWare Server 2 <em>[2 days]</em>\n</li><li>Develop solutions to VMWare Server 2 problems <em>[2 days]</em>\n<ul>\n<li>VMWare chowning VM files to root\n</li><li>Registering datastore paths\n</li></ul>\n</li></ul>\n\n<p></p></li><li>Improve failure recovery.\n<ul>\n<li>Define failure scenarios we want to handle <em>[1 day]</em>\n<ul>\n<li>Can we institute a lease with the VM software or the VM itself?\n</li><li>Can we assume Condor is the only client starting VMs?</li></ul>\n</li></ul>\n</li></ol>\n</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<hr/>\n<em>2010-Oct-20 15:59:08 by jfrey:</em> <br/>\n\nBulk change of target version from v070504 to v070505 using ./ticket-target-mover.\n<hr/>\n<em>2011-Jan-27 14:21:33 by danb:</em> <br/>\n\nBulk change of target version from v070505 to v070506 using ./ticket-target-mover.\n<hr/>\n<em>2011-Feb-01 14:49:30 by tannenba:</em> <br/>\n\nBulk change of target version from v070506 to NULL using ./ticket-target-mover.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=272\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('272'); return false;\" title=\"condor_vm_vmware.pl language dependent (bug on German system)\">#272</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"